{
  "id": "adv_card_szk_05_02",
  "title": "兵藤雫 2話 グッジョブお兄ちゃん",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "レッスンお疲れ様、雫\n今は休憩中か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good job on the lesson‚ Shizuku.\nAre you on break right now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.8000002067,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6.6666667779
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、お疲れ様、です……\nちょっと涼みたくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ thank you…\nI just wanted to cool off a bit…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.4666667779,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "少し、頭も冷やしたかった、から……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wanted to clear my head a little bit‚ too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.833333381,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "何かあったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is something wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.1000009378,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.8333334605
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "何かあった訳じゃ、ない……\nでも……うーん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not like something happened…\nBut… um…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.0666667144,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.833333381
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……良ければ、聞かせてくれないか？\n今回は担当じゃないが、話を聞くくらいは出来るよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…If it's okay‚ could you tell me?\nI'm not in charge this time‚ but I can listen.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.3471994479,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.3333356698
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "……私、お姉ちゃんだし、頑張ろうって思ってたのに\nグループの中で、うまく動けてなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Even though I thought I could do it because I'm the big sister…\nI can't seem to fit in well within the group…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.2333356698,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "みんなを支えたい、サポートしたい……\nその気持ちは、変わらない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to support everyone‚ to help out…\nThat feeling hasn't changed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.9666730722,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.5333425363
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "だけど、うまく動けない……\n動けないっていうか、言えない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I can't seem to fit in well…\nOr rather‚ I can't speak up…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.1666758697,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "どういうことだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.6000086944,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.1000081857
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "練習の時って、アイデアを出し合ったり\n意見をぶつけて、良くしていく、よね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "During practice‚ we brainstorm ideas…\nand we exchange opinions to make things better… right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.0666748524,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "でも、私は、言葉が出てこなくて……\nどう思う？　って聞かれても、答えられなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I can't find the words…\nEven when asked what I think‚ I can't answer…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.8000076771,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.7666733265
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "別のグループだと、考え方も、練習方法も\nお互いに、違いがある……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Each group has its own way of\nthinking and practicing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.0000066598,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "特に、リズノワとか、トリエルは……\nグループそのものが、先輩……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Especially LizNoir and TRINITYAiLE…\nThey're seniors in the industry…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.6000076771,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.5666718006
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "だから、かな……普段は平気でも、お仕事になると\nなんだか、恐れ多くなっちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So maybe… even though I'm usually okay‚ when it comes to work…\nI feel somewhat intimidated…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.4666718006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、尊敬しているから\n逆に言えないこともあるか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ because you respect them‚\nthere might be things you can't say in return.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.5999975045,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.8666636626
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "本当は、みんなの力になりたい……\n特にすみれちゃんは、何か悩んでるみたいだし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I really want to be of help to everyone…\nEspecially Sumire-chan‚ who seems troubled…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.7333303292,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.4333303292
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02-szk014.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、芸歴はすみれちゃんの方が長いし……\n余計な口出しは、しない方がいいのかな、とか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But Sumire-chan has more experience in the industry…\nMaybe it's better not to interfere unnecessarily…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.1999969959,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02-szk015.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたらいいんだろう……\nずっと考えてるけど……分からない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What should I do…\nI've been thinking about it‚ but…I don't know…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.5153171791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.5333145618
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（芸歴の長さか。確かに業界では大事なことだ）\n（他のグループを尊敬しているのもいいことだが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Experience does matter. Indeed‚ it's crucial in the industry）\n（It's good to respect other groups‚ but…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.7666478951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 142.5333043892
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、そうだな……例えばだけど\n雫は、遙子さんが悩んでいたら、どうする？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ yeah… for example‚ though…\nIf Haruka-san were troubled‚ what would you do‚ Shizuku?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.1333043892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02-szk016.m4a",
      "text": "解決出来るか、分からないけど……\nどうしたのか聞いて、相談に乗ってあげたい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not sure if I can solve it…\nBut I want to ask what's wrong and help…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.4666428088,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 158.4999761421
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてそう思うんだ？\n遙子さんは雫より年齢も芸歴も先輩だぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why do you feel that way?\nHaruka-san is older and has more experience than you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.4666428088,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 164.3999761421
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_02-szk017.m4a",
      "text": "そんなの、関係ない……\nだって、遙子さんは同じグループの、仲間……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That doesn't matter…\nBecause Haruka-san is a fellow member of the same group…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.5666428088,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 171.366647895
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
